---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Doing Good">
  <div class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Doing Good</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Philanthropy, impact, and making the world a little better.</p>

      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Why This Matters</h2>
        <p>
          Add your philosophy on giving, impact, and making a difference here.
          What motivates you? What frameworks do you use for thinking about impact?
        </p>

        <h2>Causes I Care About</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Cause area one — brief description</li>
          <li>Cause area two — brief description</li>
          <li>Cause area three — brief description</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Organizations I Support</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#">Organization One</a> — what they do and why</li>
          <li><a href="#">Organization Two</a> — what they do and why</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Resources</h2>
        <p>
          If you want to get started with effective giving, here are some resources
          I recommend.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://www.givewell.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GiveWell</a> — evidence-based giving recommendations</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.givingwhatwecan.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Giving What We Can</a> — pledging to give effectively</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .subtitle {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
</style>
